snippet.title: Samba Hero - Enchant Jam #1
snippet.description:
This weekend we participated in Enchant Jam #1, where we had to build a game to the rhythm of Samba. To play Samba Hero for free, access the following link: https://adrianopessoa.itch.io/samba-hero
We hope you have fun and get a great score! :)
